036/**
037 * Event handler implementation for the {@link LipidMapsParser}.
038 *
039 * @author Dominik Kopczynski
040 * @author Nils Hoffmann
041 */
042public class LipidMapsParserEventHandler extends LipidBaseParserEventHandler {
043
044    private boolean omitFa;
045    private int dbNumbers;
046    private int dbPosition;
047    private String dbCistrans;
048    private String modText;
049    private int modPos;
050    private int modNum;
051    private boolean addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer;
052
053    private static final Set<String> HEAD_GROUP_EXCEPTIONS = Set.of("PA", "PC", "PE", "PG", "PI", "PS");
054    private static final Map<String, Integer> ACER_HEADS = Map.ofEntries(
055        entry("1-O-myristoyl", 14),
056        entry("1-O-palmitoyl", 16),
057        entry("1-O-stearoyl", 18),
058        entry("1-O-eicosanoyl", 20),
059        entry("1-O-behenoyl", 22),
060        entry("1-O-lignoceroyl", 24),
061        entry("1-O-cerotoyl", 26),
062        entry("1-O-pentacosanoyl", 25),
063        entry("1-O-carboceroyl", 28),
064        entry("1-O-tricosanoyl", 30),
065        entry("1-O-lignoceroyl-omega-linoleoyloxy", 24),
066        entry("1-O-stearoyl-omega-linoleoyloxy", 18)
067    );
068
069    /**
070     * Create a new {@code LipidMapsParserEventHandler}.
071     *
072     * @param knownFunctionalGroups the known functional groups
073     */
074    public LipidMapsParserEventHandler(KnownFunctionalGroups knownFunctionalGroups) {
075        super(knownFunctionalGroups);
076        try {
077            registeredEvents = Map.ofEntries(
078                entry("lipid_pre_event", this::resetParser),
079                entry("lipid_post_event", this::buildLipid),
080
081                // set adduct events
082                entry("adduct_info_pre_event", this::newAdduct),
083                entry("adduct_pre_event", this::addAdduct),
084                entry("charge_pre_event", this::addCharge),
085                entry("charge_sign_pre_event", this::addChargeSign),
086
087                entry("mediator_pre_event", this::mediatorEvent),
088
089                entry("sgl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
090                entry("species_fa_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
091                entry("tgl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
092                entry("dpl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
093                entry("cl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
094                entry("dsl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
095                entry("fa2_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
096                entry("fa3_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
097                entry("fa4_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
098                entry("hg_dg_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
099                entry("fa_lpl_molecular_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
100                entry("hg_lbpa_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
101
102                entry("fa_no_hg_pre_event", this::pureFa),
103
104                entry("hg_sgl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
105                entry("hg_gl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
106                entry("hg_cl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
107                entry("hg_dpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
108                entry("hg_lpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
109                entry("hg_threepl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
110                entry("hg_fourpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
111                entry("hg_dsl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
112                entry("hg_cpa_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
113                entry("ch_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
114                entry("hg_che_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
115                entry("mediator_const_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
116                entry("pk_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
117                entry("hg_fa_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
118                entry("hg_lsl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
119                entry("special_cer_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
120                entry("special_cer_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
121                entry("omega_linoleoyloxy_Cer_pre_event", this::setOmegaHeadGroupName),
122
123                entry("lcb_pre_event", this::newLcb),
124                entry("lcb_post_event", this::cleanLcb),
125                entry("fa_pre_event", this::newFa),
126                entry("fa_post_event", this::appendFa),
127
128                entry("glyco_struct_pre_event", this::addGlyco),
129
130                entry("db_single_position_pre_event", this::setIsomericLevel),
131                entry("db_single_position_post_event", this::addDbPosition),
132                entry("db_position_number_pre_event", this::addDbPositionNumber),
133                entry("cistrans_pre_event", this::addCistrans),
134
135                entry("ether_pre_event", this::addEther),
136                entry("hydroxyl_pre_event", this::addHydroxyl),
137                entry("hydroxyl_lcb_pre_event", this::addHydroxylLcb),
138                entry("db_count_pre_event", this::addDoubleBonds),
139                entry("carbon_pre_event", this::addCarbon),
140
141                entry("structural_mod_pre_event", this::setStructuralSubspeciesLevel),
142                entry("single_mod_pre_event", this::setMod),
143                entry("mod_text_pre_event", this::setModText),
144                entry("mod_pos_pre_event", this::setModPos),
145                entry("mod_num_pre_event", this::setModNum),
146                entry("single_mod_post_event", this::addFunctionalGroup),
147                entry("special_cer_prefix_pre_event", this::addAcer)
148            );
149        } catch (Exception e) {
150            throw new LipidParsingException("Cannot initialize LipidMapsParserEventHandler.");
151        }
152    }
153
154    @Override
155    protected void resetParser(TreeNode node) {
156        content = null;
157        level = LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE;
158        headGroup = "";
159        lcb = null;
160        adduct = null;
161        faList.clear();
162        currentFa = null;
163        useHeadGroup = false;
164        omitFa = false;
165        dbPosition = 0;
166        dbNumbers = -1;
167        dbCistrans = "";
168        modPos = -1;
169        modNum = 1;
170        modText = "";
171        headgroupDecorators.clear();
172        addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer = false;
173    }
174
175    private void addAcer(TreeNode node) {
176        String head = node.getText();
177        headGroup = "ACer";
178
179        if (!ACER_HEADS.containsKey(head)) {
180            throw new LipidException("ACer head group '" + head + "' unknown");
181        }
182
183        HeadgroupDecorator hgd = new HeadgroupDecorator("decorator_acyl", -1, 1, null, true, knownFunctionalGroups);
184        int acer_num = ACER_HEADS.get(head);
185        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("decorator_acyl", new ArrayList<>());
186        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("decorator_acyl").add(new FattyAcid("FA", acer_num, knownFunctionalGroups));
187        headgroupDecorators.add(hgd);
188
189        if (head.equals("1-O-lignoceroyl-omega-linoleoyloxy") || head.equals("1-O-stearoyl-omega-linoleoyloxy")) {
190            addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer = true;
191        }
192    }
193
194    private void setMolecularSubspeciesLevel(TreeNode node) {
195        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.MOLECULAR_SPECIES);
196    }
197
198    private void pureFa(TreeNode node) {
199        headGroup = "FA";
200    }
201
202    private void mediatorEvent(TreeNode node) {
203        useHeadGroup = true;
204        headGroup = node.getText();
205    }
206
207    private void setIsomericLevel(TreeNode node) {
208        dbPosition = 0;
209        dbCistrans = "";
210    }
211
212    private void addDbPosition(TreeNode node) {
213        if (currentFa != null) {
214            currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(dbPosition, dbCistrans);
215
216            if (!dbCistrans.equals("E") && !dbCistrans.equals("Z")) {
217                setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
218            }
219
220        }
221    }
222
223    private void setOmegaHeadGroupName(TreeNode node) {
224        addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer = true;
225        setHeadGroupName(node);
226    }
227
228    private void addGlyco(TreeNode node) {
229        String glyco_name = node.getText();
230        HeadgroupDecorator functional_group = null;
231        try {
232            functional_group = (HeadgroupDecorator) knownFunctionalGroups.get(glyco_name);
233        } catch (Exception e) {
234            throw new LipidParsingException("Carbohydrate '" + glyco_name + "' unknown");
235        }
236
237        functional_group.getElements().put(Element.O, functional_group.getElements().get(Element.O) - 1);
238        headgroupDecorators.add(functional_group);
239    }
240
241    private void addDbPositionNumber(TreeNode node) {
242        dbPosition = Integer.valueOf(node.getText());
243    }
244
245    private void addCistrans(TreeNode node) {
246        dbCistrans = node.getText();
247    }
248
249    private void setHeadGroupName(TreeNode node) {
250        headGroup = node.getText();
251    }
252
253    private void setSpeciesLevel(TreeNode node) {
254        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SPECIES);
255    }
256
257    private void setStructuralSubspeciesLevel(TreeNode node) {
258        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
259    }
260
261    private void setMod(TreeNode node) {
262        modText = "";
263        modPos = -1;
264        modNum = 1;
265    }
266
267    private void setModText(TreeNode node) {
268        modText = node.getText();
269    }
270
271    private void setModPos(TreeNode node) {
272        modPos = node.getInt();
273    }
274
275    private void setModNum(TreeNode node) {
276        modNum = node.getInt();
277    }
278
279    private void addFunctionalGroup(TreeNode node) {
280        if (!modText.equals("Cp")) {
281            FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get(modText);
282            functional_group.setPosition(modPos);
283            functional_group.setCount(modNum);
284            String fg_name = functional_group.getName();
285            if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fg_name)) {
286                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fg_name, new ArrayList<>());
287            }
288            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fg_name).add(functional_group);
289        } else {
290            currentFa.setNumCarbon(currentFa.getNumCarbon() + 1);
291            Cycle cycle = new Cycle(3, modPos, modPos + 2, knownFunctionalGroups);
292            if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cy")) {
293                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("cy", new ArrayList<>());
294            }
295            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cy").add(cycle);
296        }
297    }
298
299    private void newFa(TreeNode node) {
300        dbNumbers = -1;
301        currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", knownFunctionalGroups);
302    }
303
304    private void newLcb(TreeNode node) {
305        lcb = new FattyAcid("LCB", knownFunctionalGroups);
306        lcb.setType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR);
307        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
308        currentFa = lcb;
309    }
310
311    private void cleanLcb(TreeNode node) {
312        if (dbNumbers > -1 && dbNumbers != currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds()) {
313            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
314        }
315        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
316            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
317        }
318        currentFa = null;
319    }
320
321    private void appendFa(TreeNode node) {
322        if (dbNumbers > -1 && dbNumbers != currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds()) {
323            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
324        }
325        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
326            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
327        }
328
329        if (currentFa.getNumCarbon() == 0) {
330            omitFa = true;
331        }
332        faList.add(currentFa);
333        currentFa = null;
334    }
335
336    private void addEther(TreeNode node) {
337        String ether = node.getText();
338        if (ether.equals("O-")) {
339            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMANYL);
340        } else if (ether.equals("P-")) {
341            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMENYL);
342        }
343    }
344
345    private void addHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
346        int num_h = node.getInt();
347
348        if (spRegularLcb()) {
349            num_h -= 1;
350        }
351
352        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
353        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
354        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
355            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
356        }
357        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
358    }
359
360    private void addHydroxylLcb(TreeNode node) {
361        String hydroxyl = node.getText();
362        int num_h = 0;
363        if (hydroxyl.equals("m")) {
364            num_h = 1;
365        } else if (hydroxyl.equals("d")) {
366            num_h = 2;
367        } else if (hydroxyl.equals("t")) {
368            num_h = 3;
369        }
370
371        if (spRegularLcb()) {
372            num_h -= 1;
373        }
374
375        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
376        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
377        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
378            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
379        }
380        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
381    }
382
383    private void addDoubleBonds(TreeNode node) {
384        currentFa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() + node.getInt());
385    }
386
387    private void addCarbon(TreeNode node) {
388        currentFa.setNumCarbon(node.getInt());
389    }
390
391    private void buildLipid(TreeNode node) {
392        if (omitFa && HEAD_GROUP_EXCEPTIONS.contains(headGroup)) {
393            headGroup = "L" + headGroup;
394        }
395
396        if (lcb != null) {
397            faList.add(0, lcb);
398        }
399       
400        Headgroup headgroup = prepareHeadgroupAndChecks();
401        content = new LipidAdduct(assembleLipid(headgroup), adduct);
402    }
403
404    private void newAdduct(TreeNode node) {
405        adduct = new Adduct("", "");
406    }
407
408    private void addAdduct(TreeNode node) {
409        adduct.setAdductString(node.getText());
410    }
411
412    private void addCharge(TreeNode node) {
413        adduct.setCharge(Integer.valueOf(node.getText()));
414    }
415
416    private void addChargeSign(TreeNode node) {
417        String sign = node.getText();
418        if (sign.equals("+")) {
419            adduct.setChargeSign(1);
420        } else if (sign.equals("-")) {
421            adduct.setChargeSign(-1);
422        }
423    }
